04:25.807 --> 04:26.766
Right.

04:29.018 --> 04:30.311
It's not the worst thing,

04:30.895 --> 04:32.188
paying the price.

04:33.690 --> 04:34.524
Yeah.

04:35.900 --> 04:38.444
