04:45.118 --> 04:48.246
Hi. I'm still here. [laughing]

04:48.329 --> 04:49.205
You are.

04:50.039 --> 04:51.624
And you're freaking out.

04:51.708 --> 04:53.167
No. I'm not.

04:53.251 --> 04:55.003
Yeah, feels like you are a little bit.

04:55.086 --> 04:56.421
And I get it.

04:56.504 --> 05:00.675
You're with somebody new,
and it's scary and weird.

05:01.175 --> 05:03.136
I think all we can really do is...

05:04.512 --> 05:05.513
dance it out.

05:06.806 --> 05:07.849
No, what?

05:07.932 --> 05:09.684
-I think we should dance it out.
-Um--

05:09.767 --> 05:10.685
Come on, little lady.

05:11.227 --> 05:12.937
Yeah, that's what we're gonna do.

05:13.021 --> 05:14.564
