-What are we doing?

05:14.647 --> 05:15.732
[laughs]

05:16.524 --> 05:18.109
<i>♪ You're wigging out</i> <i> ♪</i>

05:18.985 --> 05:20.486
<i>♪ Baby, that's all right</i> <i> </i>♪

05:21.571 --> 05:24.949
