05:25.366 --> 05:28.536
<i>♪ Especially when</i>
<i>He's a nerdy chiropractor</i>  <i>♪</i>

05:29.829 --> 05:33.833
<i>♪ Well, maybe it'll help</i>
<i>If you knew just one factor</i>  ♪

05:34.792 --> 05:37.795
<i>♪ He thinks you're incredible</i>  ♪

05:38.838 --> 05:40.173
<i>♪ And...</i> <i> ♪</i>

05:41.215 --> 05:44.218
